A huge cask of Rootweal, a heady red wine from the Yuirwood region of Aglarond.

Price: 7 GP
Quality: 4
Strength: 2

Value.value: A smooth, full-bodied wine the color of red silk. It originates from the Yuirwood in Aglarond and has a flavor best described as that of 'a forest meadow alive in the glad light of the sun'.
